Privacy Policy
Introduction
Welcome to Team up App. We are committed to protecting your privacy and ensuring that your personal information is handled in a safe and responsible manner. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard your information when you use our App.
1. Information We Collect
When you use our App, we collect the following types of personal information:
• Name: To identify you within our app.
• Gender: To tailor content and communications.
• Phone Number: We use your phone number to:
o Authenticate your identity and provide secure access to your account
o Send you verification codes and account-related notifications
o Improve the security of our app
o For communication purposes related to team activities and updates.
• Location: To provide location-based features and services.
• Date of Birth: To verify your age and tailor content accordingly.
• Photos and videos: When you use our app to upload or share photos and videos, we collect the content of the photos and videos you upload. We use your photos and videos for the following purposes:
o To display and share your content within the app
o To enhance and personalize your user experience
o To analyze usage patterns and improve our app's features and services
2. How We Use Your Information
We use the collected information solely for the following purposes:
• Communication: To contact you regarding team activities, updates, and other important information related to the sports team.
• Personalization: To tailor content and interactions based on your preferences and profile information.
3.Data Storage and Security
We implement appropriate technical and organizational measures to protect your personal information(phone number ,Dates of birth) from unauthorized access, disclosure, alteration, or destruction. Your data is stored securely on our servers and is accessible only to authorized personnel.
4. Data Sharing
We share all the information we collect with other users, except for phone numbers and dates of birth. We do not share, sell, or disclose your personal information(phone number, Dates of birth) to any third parties, other apps, or users. Your information remains confidential and is used solely for the purposes described in this Privacy Policy.
We may share your photos and videos in the following circumstances:
• Within the App: Your content may be visible to other users .
5. Data Retention
We retain your personal information for as long as necessary to fulfill the purposes for which it was collected, including for legal, accounting, or reporting requirements. If you wish to have your data deleted, please contact us as described in the “Contact Us” section below.
6. Your Rights
You have the right to access, update, or delete your personal information. If you wish to exercise these rights or have any questions about how your data is handled, please contact us using the information provided below.
7.Children's Privacy
We are committed to protecting the privacy of children who use our app. If you are a parent or guardian, please review the following information:
• Information Collection: We collect the same types of information (name, age, gender ,location, phone number ,dates of birth) from children as we do from adults.
• Parental Consent: We obtain verifiable parental consent before collecting personal information from children under 18. Parents can review, update, or request the deletion of their child’s information by contacting us at operations@wyndtechnologies.com.
• Data Usage: The information collected from children is used in the same ways as described in this Privacy Policy, including for app functionality and communication.
8. Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time to reflect changes in our practices or for other operational, legal, or regulatory reasons. We will notify you of any significant changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on our App.
9. Contact Us
If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy or our data practices, please contact us at:
• Address: WYND Technologies Private Limited,#372,3rd Floor, Cabin No305, 6thCross,Golden Square ,Wilson Garden, Banglore 560027
10. Acceptance of This Privacy Policy
By using our App, you consent to the terms of this Privacy Policy. If you do not agree with our practices, please do not use our App.
